CatchyOS setup when installing or default settings taking place:
1. Install github-cli, btop gpu lib, git
2. Turn off system sound
3. Overwrite .bashrc
4. Arrange the default apps
5. Change cursor size: Settings/Global theme/Pointer/Size 42
